Been following this unprofessional idiot&#39;s items for awhile now. I love how he says that Frank charges thousands of dollars for an original Frank&#39;s box. 

This dude is the worst type of con, preying on people who know only enough to be familiar with the term Frank&#39;s box. Then again, it always has bothered me when people take shack hacks and charge stupid prices for them on ebay under the Frank&#39;s box moniker.

This guy is based out of Nevada I believe, and his group&#39;s ethics leave little to be desired. Takes all kinds, I reckon...

Andy


